data.description: MOVE IN READY!  !!!RV PARKING!!!  LARGE BACKYARD!  4 BED. 3 BATH. 2 CAR GARAGE.  NEW INTERIOR PAINT, CARPET AND LVP.  THIS HOME OFFERS A SPACIOUS OPEN LAYOUT WITH VAULTED CEILINGS IN FAMILY ROOM AND MASTER, LARGE LIVING ROOM ON THE MAIN AND FAMILY ROOM ON THE LOWER, WITH GAS FIREPLACE, THAT WALKS OUT TO THE LARGE BACKYARD. ON THE UPPER LEVEL YOU WILL FIND THREE OF THE FOUR BEDROOMS--INCLUDING THE MASTER WITH DEDICATED MASTER BATH. MOVE DOWN TO THE LOWEST LEVEL AND YOU WILL FIND THE FOURTH BEDROOM AND BATHROOM. NEW ROOF IN 2019. HOT WATER HEATER IN 2023.  SPRINKLER SYSTEM IN FRONT.  SECURITY SYSTEM.  EASY COMMUTE TO FT. CARSON, PETERSON AFB & SCHRIEVER.  DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS OPPORTUNITY!!!
